  m_text: "It's 3am.\r\nalone in a small apartment in the city.\r\na job that pays
    the bills and nothing else.\r\nused to have hobbies. stopped.\r \ncan't remember
    why.\r\ncan't sleep.\r\npicks up the phone.\r \njust for a minute.\r\noutside,
    something is happening.\r\nthe feed knows. it always knows.\r\n\r_____________________________________________\nscroll
    the feed to unlock the apartment.\r\nsleep when you can't take it anymore.\r\nthe
    deeper you scroll, the worse it gets."
